Task: Batch SRS queue resolution to eliminate N+1 queries

Summary: Refactored convex/queue/queue.ts to replace sequential per-item database lookups with batched parallel reads.

Changes:
- Replaced resolveQueueItem (sequential per-item) with resolveQueueItems (bulk parallel)
- Standard document lookups now use Promise.all over deduplicated IDs
- Practice item queries now use Promise.all over unique problemFamilyIds
- Activity lookups now use Promise.all over deduplicated activity IDs
- Added .take(100) defensive bound to srs_cards query
- Added 3 new tests verifying batched call patterns

